		</div>
		<p>I have some ancient aloe plants in my yard and a couple in my kitchen.  I learned about it&#8217;s healing properties in nursing school in 1975.  The instructor said the Indians called it Medicine Plant.  I use it for burns and cuts, and it works like magic.<br />
The taste isn&#8217;t wonderful, but considering what it can do for us, it&#8217;s worth ingesting.  Thanks for the tip on camouflaging the taste.</p>
		</div>
</li>
		<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 clearfix" id="comment-4692">
		<div id="div-comment-4692" class="clearfix comment-container">
		<div class="comment-author vcard">
		<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/989d4524009eb5d33f1ac718dd2992b4?s=55&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-55 photo' height='55' width='55' />		<span class="authorname">Spud</span>
		</div>
				<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<a href="http://www.veggie-wedgie.com/?p=827&amp;cpage=1#comment-4692">
		July 14, 2009 at 13:52</a>
        		 
		</div>
		<p>&#8220;I had 3 spots that would not leave for a week and after I apply the Aloe, they got smaller and started healing!&#8221;</p>
<p>Really? That&#8217;s intriguing&#8230; Most spots would begin to heal after about a week anyway&#8230;.</p>
		</div>
</li>
		<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1 clearfix" id="comment-4719">
		<div id="div-comment-4719" class="clearfix comment-container">
		<div class="comment-author vcard">
		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e4c5c1d72a0c27bd96fbad3190aae945?s=55&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-55 photo' height='55' width='55' />		<span class="authorname">pariah</span>
		</div>
				<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
		<a href="http://www.veggie-wedgie.com/?p=827&amp;cpage=1#comment-4719">
		July 16, 2009 at 01:38</a>
        		 
		</div>
		<p>My father died the other day. I rubbed some fresh Aloe on him and he came back to life. This is amazing. magical stuff.</p>
		</div>
</li>
		<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 clearfix" id="comment-4743">
		<div id="div-comment-4743" class="clearfix comment-container">
